        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 19 of the SLEEP program. The script works on the specific pattern of treating peace as a threat, bracing in the quiet for the thing that hasn't arrived yet. The karate chop names that pattern directly.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
